{"tid":2315152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反省下啦！阿迪達！","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:10:37.000Z","uid":38189,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"391baad21853a3ccf1dc569b62960d9db15ecbf5","tid":2315152,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴支持共產黨，支持國民教育，支持清算新疆，支持習大大，全部都是你做，賣港賊就是阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n基奧特退廠、卡蘇拿退廠，一直到最近禾確特退廠、伊和比退廠，高斯尼退黨，中間有米希達恩退廠、藍斯退廠，馬天尼斯退廠，這不是分裂嗎，本來就是離離合合，雲加有份起球場，現在都反佢，有甚麼所謂。<br />\n<br />\n甚麼叫partey走場，為何要諉過他人，你自己不是分裂自己嗎？自己不反省所做的事，而諉過他人。<br />\n<br />\n為何你只得第15名！由排第1變第15，反省一下，阿迪達！"},{"pid":"6725121e4d589193a2b4bb8c84e7c5820b6e7253","tid":2315152,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727e311e68235db9b5d3f9d3c7c30221b61b00c0","tid":2315152,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa527cd6f18ddbd132a625a90dcec1407bf325d","tid":2315152,"uid":11903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4f28f2860a39684ac97b7c5cf2388ecb6edeaa","tid":2315152,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"比時間達SIR啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9582b4e133e2a90c759e159ae8b0776004d3629","tid":2315152,"uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"好彩今季般茅降左班<br />\n阿狗都叫有第一可以上下"},{"pid":"70eadc72e13aad147c30a79014636cca42e338d1","tid":2315152,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime